				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">So you know what you are really up against:
<br />

<br />
Pet is going to be eaten alive in Qvic -- 1100-1295 quad hitters that are (sometimes SoW-ed) adds. Some are hasted (shaman class). About 1/3 of the mobs are yellow /cons.
<br />

<br />
Think the last field before Tables in PoFire crossed with LDoN Hard.
<br />

<br />
Add to that the inadequacy of a 1200-point heal, or 2146-point Mend compared to mobs that can and will do 4000+ damage to the pet in a single round.
<br />

<br />
This is an add that ran into camp and latched onto my pet. MS4, DPoC, full buffs as we had just wiped and been re-buffed (Pet Affinity):
