				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I think having pet heals overhauled is one point all mages would agree on. I would much rather give this top priority than most other discussions on what needs to be done, as it is not so much a new feature that needs to be added but an old problem that needs to be fixed. 
<br />

<br />
And I agree with Naladini, giving us better heals benefits us without stepping on other classes toes, and encourages keeping the pet alive, which is how I have always played my mage. I am all for more pet mitigation, more pet dps etc (in that order), but given the choice I would put my money on the heals as first thing to fix. 
<br />

<br />
Excellent post, may the powers that be take note.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
